title.rendered: Luxurious 4BHK Apartment For Sale & Rent In Anand Niketan

content.rendered:
Located in one of the most prestigious locations in #southDelhi. This mesmerizing stylish & modern 400sqyds apartment has four dreamy bedrooms with connected bathrooms, a fully equipped Italian modular kitchen, a fully automatic lift, imported bathroom fittings with rain shower head and Jacuzzi, VRV air conditioning, and stilt car parking.
♕4bhk
♕2nd Floor
♕400sqyds
♕2100sqft
♕Fully Equipped Modular Kitchen
♕Imported Bathroom Fittings
♕VRV Air-conditioners
♕For Sale 9CR
♕For Rent: 2.5Lakhs

Sunil Bhandari
Call On 98100-05193 For a Site Visit!
http://wa.me/919810005193
ROYALE REALTORS INDIA
https://www.royalerealtorsindia.com
19 DDA Market, Shanti Niketan, New Delhi, Delhi 110021

Checkout Our Other Listings Here
Follow @royalerealtorsindia on social media
